# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# PTO Central — publish guard.
# This repo deploys to PUBLIC GitHub Pages (mybasepay.github.io/pto-central).
# Anything committed here becomes publicly downloadable. Internal working
# material stays local, matching the original publish precedent (the repo has
# only ever contained the app surface: pages, js/, lib/, components/).
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Internal documentation, flow notes, and provisioning scripts (contain
# process details, item ids, and names — keep off the public site).
docs/
flows/
scripts/
PTO_CENTRAL_ARCHITECTURE.md

# Dev/diagnostic pages (localhost-only; not linked from the app).
dev-*.html
serve.json

# Placeholder modules for future phases (not loaded by any published page).
js/calendar.js
js/notify.js
js/pages/hr-dashboard.page.js
js/pages/hr-employee.page.js

# Editor / local tooling.
.vscode/
